com.cse3111project.bot.spring.model.engine.marker

Interface SQLAccessible

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Course, courseDetailsSyncDB, CreditTransfer, ExamCreditTransfer, LocalInstitutionCreditTransfer, Minibus, NonLocalInstitutionCreditTransfer, Recreation, Societies, Staff

    public interface SQLAccessible
    The SQLAccessible Interface implements the structure for class to get data from SQL database if there is any available to the class.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.lang.String getDataFromSQL()
      This abstract method will execute SQL query at a single thread and get the data from SQL database.

    • Method Detail

      • getDataFromSQL

        java.lang.String getDataFromSQL()
                         throws NotSQLAccessibleError,
                                java.net.URISyntaxException,
                                java.sql.SQLException
        This abstract method will execute SQL query at a single thread and get the data from SQL database. It is supposed to be implemented in the class that implemented this interface.
        Returns:
        String This method will return the query result in String format
        Throws:
        NotSQLAccessibleError
        java.net.URISyntaxException
        java.sql.SQLException
